				<section id='overview'>
					<hr class='indent' /><h5>Shop Smarter</h5>
					<p>SmartCart guides shoppers through grocery stores. The android tablet and enclosure allows buyers to scan items at their own pace and preference, accommodating different modes of shopping from predetermined lists to impulse buying. With SmartCart, there's no need for checkout lines - simply exit the store and confirm the final payment. </p>

					<div class='video-wrapper'>
