					</div>

				</section>

				<section id='prototyping'>
					<hr class='indent' /><h5>Prototyping</h5>
					<p>Needfinding in this project began with talking with shoppers about supermarket frustrations, following their shopping habits, and talking with employees about self-checkout hassles and inefficiencies. After considering a number of <a href='http://smartcart247.weebly.com/prototyping.html'>prototypes</a>, we decided on a tablet app. 
					</p>

					<figure>
						<img src='images/smartcart/007.png' />
