					</figure>

				</section>

				<section id='user-testing'>
					<hr class='indent' /><h5>User Testing</h5>
					<p>From <a href='http://smartcart247.weebly.com/user-testing.html'>user testing</a>, several interface issues were highlighted, but most prominent was the ambiguity found in checking out. Shoppers were reminded of an online experience, instead of a physical store. We added additional dialogues and more obvious actions to simplify the checkout process. </p>

					<figure>
						<img src='images/smartcart/smartcartHiDef.jpg'>
						<figcaption>high-fidelity mockup of list &amp; map view</figcaption>
					</figure>

					<p>Aside from <a href='http://smartcart247.weebly.com/functional-2.html'>new features</a> to add to the app, user testing also revealed that shoppers found it very difficult to use the SmartCart application in coordination with the physical cart. The tablet seemed more like a peripheral accessory than an integrated shopping cart helper, so we designed a hardware enclosure to ease use and accessibility of the touchscreen.</p>

